  "page": "Urrathon IV Goodbrother",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\"><img alt=\"House Goodbrother.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/50px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/75px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/100px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Urrathon IV Goodbrother<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Badbrother</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\"><img alt=\"House Goodbrother.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/50px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/75px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/100px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nUrrathon Goodbrother, Fourth of His Name Since the <a href=\"/index.php/Grey_King\" title=\"Grey King\">Grey King</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"King of the Iron Islands\">High King</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Predecessor</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Urragon_III_Greyiron\" title=\"Urragon III Greyiron\">Urragon III Greyiron</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Successor</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Torgon_Greyiron\" title=\"Torgon Greyiron\">Torgon Greyiron</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nBadbrother</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\">House Goodbrother</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Urrathon IV Goodbrother</b>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup> also known as <b>Badbrother</b>, was a <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"King of the Iron Islands\">High King</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a> who ruled during the <a href=\"/index.php/Age_of_Heroes\" title=\"Age of Heroes\">Age of Heroes</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Urrathon_IV_Goodbrother&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Urrathon was mean and savagely cruel, often displaying arrogance and impiety.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Urrathon_IV_Goodbrother&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>When King <a href=\"/index.php/Urragon_III_Greyiron\" title=\"Urragon III Greyiron\">Urragon III Greyiron</a> died, a <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsmoot\" title=\"Kingsmoot\">kingsmoot</a> was called by his family while one of the king's sons, <a href=\"/index.php/Torgon_Greyiron\" title=\"Torgon Greyiron\">Torgon Greyiron</a>, was raiding the <a href=\"/index.php/Mander\" title=\"Mander\">Mander</a>. The king's younger sons were hoping that one of them would be elected king, but the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> chose Urrathon Goodbrother of <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Wyk\" title=\"Great Wyk\">Great Wyk</a> instead. Urrathon IV's first act was to have all of the late king's sons at the kingsmoot executed. Thus Urrathon became known as \"Badbrother\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Urrathon ruled for two years and made many enemies due to his cruelty. Torgon, the only surviving son of the previous king, returned to the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a> and declared the kingsmoot decision unlawful as he had not been present to put forth his claim as was his right. The priests, <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a>, and lords rallied to Torgon's banner and Urrathon was cast down, hacked to pieces by his own captains. Torgon the Latecomer succeeded Badbrother as king.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Urrathon_IV_Goodbrother&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The first thing the new king did was command that all the sons of <a href=\"/index.php/Urragon_III_Greyiron\" title=\"Urragon III Greyiron\">the old king</a> be put to death, and so they were. After that men called him Badbrother, though in truth they'd been no kin of his.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tristifer_Botley\" title=\"Tristifer Botley\">Tristifer Botley</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Asha Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Urrathon_IV_Goodbrother&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">In <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_26\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 26\">The Wayward Bride</a>, he is called Urragon Goodbrother, whereas <i>The World of Ice &amp; Fire</i> calls him Urrathon Goodbrother (<i>The World of Ice &amp; Fire</i>, The Iron Islands: Driftwood Crowns). It has been suggested to change the spelling in <i>A Dance with Dragon</i> instead of <i>The World of Ice &amp; Fire</i>, making Urrathon the correct spelling (A Forum of Ice and Fire: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://asoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?/topic/34958-the-asoiaf-wiki-thread/&amp;do=findComment&amp;comment=8078469\">The ASOIAF wiki thread (November 20, 2017)</a>).</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Urrathon_IV_Goodbrother&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_26\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 26\">Chapter 26</a>, The Wayward Bride.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Iron Islands: Driftwood Crowns.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<td style=\"width:30%;\" rowspan=\"1\">Preceded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Urragon_III_Greyiron\" title=\"Urragon III Greyiron\">Urragon III Greyiron</a></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> <a href=\"/index.php/High_King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"High King of the Iron Islands\">High King of the Iron Islands</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\">Succeeded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Torgon_Greyiron\" title=\"Torgon Greyiron\">Torgon Greyiron</a></div>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403142356\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.109 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.331 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1663/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 14881/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 11312/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2036/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3209/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.200/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.42 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  317.655      1 -total\n 79.61%  252.887      1 Template:Infobox_monarch\n 7